# 🎮 Dodgy Game

Dodgy Game is a 2D arcade-style game developed using the Godot Engine, where the player must avoid incoming obstacles and survive as long as possible.

## 🚀 Features
- Smooth player movement
- Random obstacle spawning
- Collision detection system
- Score tracking

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Godot Engine
- GDScript

## ▶️ How to Run
